member.name: MIB_UDP6TABLE_OWNER_MODULE
member.summary: The MIB_UDP6TABLE_OWNER_MODULE structure contains the User Datagram Protocol (UDP) listener table for IPv6 on the local computer. The table also includes any available ownership data and the process ID (PID) that issued the call to the function for each UDP endpoint.
